abstract: >-
  DTQEM v17.0 provides a numerically exact 2x2 Lindblad model for wave‑particle 
  duality under measurement. The Hamiltonian is fixed; the observer only adds 
  pure dephasing via the DTQEM relation (gamma*t_obs = 2 ln(tan theta)). 
  The model reproduces the quantum Zeno effect and allows recovery of 
  the natural frequency via FFT. Works for both massive particles and photons.
